                type="document" xml:id="ch_d41">
                <head>CH–41. Editorial Note</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right"><date calendar="gregorian" when="1960-10-28"
                            >October 28, 1960</date></dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>By an exchange of notes at Santiago, October 28, 1960, entered into force on the
                    same date, representatives of the United States and Chile signed an agreement
                    providing for a grant of funds to Chile for purpose of disaster rehabilitation.
                    For text of the agreement, see 11 <gloss target="#t_UST_1">UST</gloss> (pt. 2)
                    2617.</p>
            </div>
